Detailed Description

cvmx_uctl::_ohci_ctl

RSL registers starting from 0x10 can be accessed only after hclk is active and hreset is deasserted.

UCTL_OHCI_CTL = UCTL OHCI Control Register This register controls the general behavior of UCTL OHCI datapath.
